  <description type="morphology">Plants 8–15 cm, (elongating in fruit).  Leaf blades 3–6 × 0.8–1 cm.  Inflorescences 3–9-flowered.  Flowers heterostylous; corolla lobes 12–25 mm.  2n = 22.</description>
